<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
   		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge">
		<title>PC端借款</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/jiekuan.css" />
		<script src="js/jquery.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="czz-top">
			<div class="abcd">
				<p class="czz-iphone">
					<i class="czz-i"></i>
					<span class="czz-z">iPhone版</span>
				</p>
				<p class="czz-az">
					<i class="czz-a"></i>
					<span class="czz-q">敬请期待</span>
				</p>
				<div class="erweima"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="czz-center">
			<div class="czz-tp">
				<img src="img/content.png" alt="" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="czz-footer">
			<div class="czzinner">
				<a href="###"><div class="czz-jk">立即借款</div></a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="czz-fcbox">
			<div class="czz-fc">
				<p style="padding-top: 28px">借款还能赚钱？</p>
				<p>马上邀请好友，立即赢取奖金，借款越多，奖金越多！</p>
				<a href="###"><div class="close"><img src="img/close.png" alt=""></div></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script>
	$(function(){
		$(".czz-jk").on('click', function (e) {
			$("html,body").animate({scrollTop:0},400);
		})
		$(".close").on('click', function (e) {
			$(".czz-fcbox").animate({width:0},200,function(){
				$(".czz-fcbox").css("display","none");
			});
		})
	})
	</script>
</html>
